title: [BUG] sporadic failure in block bootstrap transformer doctest
body:
A recent run had an unclear failure related to block bootstrap transformer:
https://github.com/alan-turing-institute/sktime/actions/runs/2687424513
This seems sporadic, not reproducible.

I can't make sense of this, what is this?
@ltsaprounis, any idea?
